                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> The Harvest is on a ceiling or wall</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The Harvest shrieks and drops onto creatures below it. It Leaps. Any creature within its space when it lands must succeed at a @Check[reflex|dc:26] save or take @Damage[5d6[bludgeoning]] damage. Creatures that critically fail their save are knocked @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Prone].</p>"
                },
