                },
                "actions": {
                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> The Harvest is within reach of a dead creature</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> The Harvest strips flesh from bone with startling precision, fusing it into its body. The Harvest gains temporary Hit Points equal to double the creature's level for 1 minute; this effect is cumulative, resetting the duration each time the ability is used, and can give the Harvest up to a maximum of 30 temporary Hit Points at a time.</p>"
                },
