                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The Harvest lets out a strained shriek that is equal parts malfunctioning robot and decaying windpipes. All creatures within 120 feet must make a @Check[will|dc:26] save or be @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Frightened]{Frightened 2} for 1 minute (@UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Frightened]{Frightened 3} on a critical failure). Creatures are then immune to Malformed Scream for 24 hours.</p>"
                },
